      "content": "KVdb is a hosted serverless key-value database with a simple REST API. Buckets are namespaces of key-value pairs accessed over HTTPS using standard methods (GET, POST, PATCH, DELETE). KVdb supports access control via secret, read, and write keys, custom Lua scripts, and per-bucket TTLs.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: KVdb",
